  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2556160/extras/bdc515c32b0efceda8b0f071e0fa3ee3.avif?t=1758133457\" width=450 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game</h2><strong>Cute Farmer Life</strong> is a cute pixel art farm simulator designed to be played at your own pace. Grow, craft, harvest and talk to the locals while you solve the mystery that hangs over the small town.<br><br>Designed to play without worries, in Cute Farmer Life you play as Matt, a cat who doesn't want to go back to the city and moves to a small house in the countryside to live on what he grows. Craft tools, grow rare plants, take care of the animals and discover all that this farm simulator offers you, where crops take seconds instead of days and there are always things to do.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics<br><strong>Grow plants, craft tools & items:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2556160/extras/df4c4b34772e23d4646622b81eef6980.poster.avif?t=1758133457\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2556160/extras/df4c4b34772e23d4646622b81eef6980.webm?t=1758133457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2556160/extras/c662d5c4650515ab00d44fa3f3c1b520.poster.avif?t=1758133457\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2556160/extras/c662d5c4650515ab00d44fa3f3c1b520.webm?t=1758133457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Animal care and much more...</strong><br><span cla